<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Horror History</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jolly+Lodger&display=swap');
      .texto {
        font-family: 'Jolly Lodger', cursive;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .btn-blood {
        font-size: 20px;
        min-width: 120px;
        background-color: rgba(156, 0, 1, 0.8);
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .btn-blood::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
        transform: skewX(-30deg);
        transition: left 0.3s;
        z-index: -1;
      }

      .btn-blood:hover::before {
        left: 100%;
      }

      .image-background {
        background-image: url('/assets/fondo.png');
        background-position: center;
        background-size: cover;
      }

      .image-back {
        opacity: 0.2;
        background-color: #1d0000;
        position: absolute;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="image-background">
    <div class="image-back h-screen"></div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-screen">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white texto">¿Estas listo para descubrir tus mayores temores?</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white texto">Aqui encontraras historias que te helaran la sangre, preparate</p>
      <button class="btn-blood mt-4 texto" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">
        Inicia la sesión
      </button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
